name: Still Alive
description:
This piece represents my daily battle with chronic depression and suicidal thoughts.
Despite everything, I am still alive, and I will carry on.

10% of the total mint fees will be converted to BTC and donated to the Association For Suicide Prevention (https://afsp.org). A receipt will be minted and airdropped to all original purchasers, and holders of the token at the time of donation!

Thanks for supporting my work!
